elements.name: Verify User will able to navigate to Petclinic application

steps.name: User will navigate to Petclinic url
User should able to see Welcome to Petclinic message
User should able to see title of the webpage

elements.name: Verify sub-menus like ALL and ADD NEW is displays on Owners tab

steps.name: User is on Petclinic home page
User clicks on owners tab
ALL and ADD NEW owners sub-menus should be displayed

elements.name: Verify user clicks on ADD NEW sub-menu on Owners tab

steps.name: User is on Owners tab
User clicks on ADD NEW sub-menu
New Owner page should get displayed

name: User going to validate New Owner Page for Petclinic application

elements.name: Verify user is able to add New Owner

steps.name: User is on New Owner page
User enter valid First Name, Last Name, Address, City, Telephone
User clicks on Add Owner button on New Owner page
User should be navigate on Owners page and added owner should be displayed at last

elements.name: Verify pet details for existing owner

steps.name: User is on All Owners list page
User clicks on existing owner name
Pets details like Name,Birth Date,Type should be displayed

elements.name: Verify sub-menus like ALL and ADD NEW is displays on Veterinarians tab

steps.name: User is on homepage and able to see veterinarians menu
User clicks on veterinarians tab
ALL and ADD NEW veterinarians sub-menus should be displayed

elements.name: Verify user clicks on ALL sub-menu on Veterinarians tab

steps.name: User is on Veterinarians tab
User clicks on ALL sub-menu
Veterinarians list should be displayed

elements.name: Verify total numbers of radiology Specialties

steps.name: User is on veterinarians page
User should see total numbers of radiology from veterinarians Specialties
